Co. plan to invest around $12.5 billion in the second expansion
phase of their joint-venture Rabigh Refining and Petrochemicals
Co., al-Hayat reported, citing an unidentified source.  The two companies will decide by the end of the year on the
expansion projectâ€™s final cost and will need three years to
complete the work, the London-based newspaper  said . The entire
Rabigh complex will cost an estimated $22.5 billion, al-Hayat
